title: Johnny Gosch /// Part 2 /// 58
description:
Johnny Gosch Part 2 ////// 58


Truecrimegarage.com


Today we cover part 2 of the disappearance of young Johnny Gosch. Last week we went through the details of Johnny going out to do his paper route early in the morning. Twice a vehicle approached Johnny and a man with dark hair and slurred speech asked him for directions. Shortly after Johnny disappeared and he has never been seen since... Or has he?


Beer of the week - Jade IPA by Foothills Brewing, Winston Salem, North Carolina

Garage Grade - 4 1/2 bottle caps out of 5
